Class Project2_Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • Project2_Parser

  • public class Project2_Parser
extends java.lang.Object
    This program implements a syntax parser for the MINI-LOL programming language. Project 2 in the CS 4323 (Compiler Construction) course at the University of Oklahoma.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Cameron

      • BOOKKEEPER

      • SCANNER

        public static int SCANNER(char c)
        Simulates a DFA. Returns a single token in Mini-LOL syntax.
        Parameters:
        c - the current character being observed by the DFA
        Returns:
        A token in the format "[type]$[token]". This will be returned as "" until a token has been fully generated.
